'''Sylvie De Caluwé''' (born 1986) is a Belgian model and television presenter,<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nieuwsblad.be/article/detail.aspx?articleid=VU1R3LRG|title=Sylvie De Caluwé maakt droom waar|last=Van Volcem|first=Steffan|date=22 April 2008|work=[[Het Nieuwsblad]]|publisher=Dutch|accessdate=10 April 2011}}</ref> born in 1986 in [[Torhout]], [[Belgium]]. She began modeling in the year 2000. Her career has since accelerated following a photo shoot for ''[[P-Magazine]]''. Since then she has also appeared in other serial publications like ''Ché'' and ''[[Maxim (magazine)|Maxim]]''.

De Caluwé appears on the [[television]] show "Gunk TV", which caters to a young audience of technophiles and gamers.

